Tested up to: 3.2.1
Stable tag: trunk
Site: http://vidcura.org

VidCura is a WordPress plugin that facilitates the creation of Roku channels.

== Description ==

VidCura is a very specific plugin. The focus is on providing tools that help facilitate the process of creating a connected TV channel. 

The first release of VidCura focuses on the Roku platform. So, in essence, VidCura is a WordPress that permits the creation of a Roku channel.

== Installation ==

1. Upload VidCura to the `/wp-content/plugins/` directory (and unzip it if necessary)
2. Activate the plugin through the 'Plugins' menu in WordPress
3. Use the VidCura and Assets menu entries to start building your channel!